        <mxCell id="7uIm9pzK7ymgNPtDu2-A-92" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Contas email" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="270" x="2130" y="297" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7uIm9pzK7ymgNPtDu2-A-118" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;Validação Data Contracts&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="169.48" x="238.52" y="1063" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7uIm9pzK7ymgNPtDu2-A-120" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Definição do Schema dos Dados deve ser feito em um JSON Schema, YAML no:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;GIT para validação de compatibilidade da versão do schema no pipeline CI/CD,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;registrar no schema Pub/Sub&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ex: &amp;lt;YAML&amp;gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;version: 1.2&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;fields:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; - name: transaction_id&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; type: string&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; required: true&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; - name: amount&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; type: decimal&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; required: true&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; constraint: &quot;&amp;gt; 0&quot;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Isso vai i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;mpedir:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Q&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;uebra silenciosa&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;- Força governança&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;- Garante rastreabilidade&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;- Reduz risco operacional&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;- Facilita auditoria&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Formaliza Data Contract&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Pelo Git pode ser controlado o versionamento do schema e validado via&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;CI/CD (pipeline deploy).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Havendo violação do contrato, pipeline CI/CD para, aciona alerta e faz rollback para o schema anteior válido.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3580&quot; data-end=&quot;3619&quot;&gt;Isso cria &lt;span data-start=&quot;3590&quot; data-end=&quot;3618&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;dupla camada de proteção&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;3621&quot; data-end=&quot;3685&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;3621&quot; data-end=&quot;3652&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3624&quot; data-end=&quot;3652&quot;&gt;Governança (antes do deploy)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;3653&quot; data-end=&quot;3685&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3656&quot; data-end=&quot;3685&quot;&gt;Bloqueio técnico (em runtime)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="255.91" x="37.59" y="1416.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7uIm9pzK7ymgNPtDu2-A-132" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Validação do Schema no Pub/Sub&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Falha no Produtor da Mensagem:&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;451&quot; data-end=&quot;470&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;453&quot; data-end=&quot;470&quot;&gt;A publicação da mensagem falha&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;471&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;473&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;A mensagem &lt;span data-start=&quot;484&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;não é levado para o tópico&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;471&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;473&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-start=&quot;484&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;Cloud Monitoring pode ser usado para alerta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;471&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;473&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-start=&quot;484&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;Corrige problema no sistema Produtor&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Falha no Consumo da mensagem:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O schema pode esta correto mas alguma validação de regra falha, por ex: valor &amp;gt; 0 e veio nulo (negativo).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Neste caso o CloudFunction encaminha o dado para uma fila de tratamento (DLQ) (pub/sub).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="230" x="345.18" y="1280" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
