        <mxCell id="7uIm9pzK7ymgNPtDu2-A-208" parent="1" style="sketch=0;html=1;verticalAlign=top;labelPosition=center;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;align=center;spacingTop=-6;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#999999;shape=image;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;BigQuery&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="60" x="2221.7" y="1690" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7uIm9pzK7ymgNPtDu2-A-210" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Modelos determinísticos (XGBoost) versus LLMs&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Modelos LLMs são probabilísticos não determinísticos, são difíceis de serem explicados os resultados gerados, não é indicado para dados numéricos além do risco de alucinação do modelo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Modelo de Risco Financeiro requerem que sejam estáveis/determinísticos, auditáveis, fácil de explicar e reproduzidos em outros ambientes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="25" width="580.82" x="1748" y="1070" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7uIm9pzK7ymgNPtDu2-A-215" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;BigQuery suporta tipo de dados Vetor e realiza busca por similaridade.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Vantagens:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Integração com dados estruturados&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Governança centralizada&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Segurança já configurada&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ideal para crédito (explicabilidade + auditoria)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="255" x="2297.8199999999997" y="1720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="4vHcD-1g2ihIS0cSqU0S-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;Arquitetura Híbrida e Qualidade de Dados (Data Quality)  &lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="358.91" x="516.09" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7uIm9pzK7ymgNPtDu2-A-121" parent="1" style="editableCssRules=.*;html=1;shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Topico schema_X&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;(Pub/Sub)&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="36" x="315.09000000000003" y="166" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Zxv30gHGLYkYmm7J4-9J-2" parent="1" style="editableCssRules=.*;html=1;shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" value="Consome Topico&lt;br&gt;Valida schema/data quality&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;(Cloud Function)&lt;/i&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="40" x="443.59000000000003" y="169.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Zxv30gHGLYkYmm7J4-9J-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;Para Dados Transacionais é necessário uma carga inicial das tabelas que serão capturados os dados. Esta carga sendo feito de forma manual (export) tem menor custo&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;, é mais controlada e rápida. A partir dai inicia o DataStream com o CDC habilitado com destino no CloudStorage que recebe o evento (PUT) e dispara&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;uma notificação no Tópico de validação de Schema da tabela. Um job consumidor (Cloud Function) checa os dados validando o Schema e qualidade dos dados.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Somente com o nível de qualidade aceitável e Schema validados será iniciado o ETL do Data Flow e ingestão no BigQuery.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Dados com quebra de contrato ou qualidade de dados reprovada são reportados em uma fila de erros para ser consumida e analisada.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="36.5" width="676.5" x="826.25" y="129.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Zxv30gHGLYkYmm7J4-9J-19" edge="1" parent="1" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" value="">
